==气候==
洛迦诺平均一年有100.7天为雨雪天气，均降雨量达{{Convert|1668|mm|in|abbr=on}}。五月为最潮湿的月份，月均降雨量达{{Convert|194|mm|in|abbr=on}}，平均每月有12.6天为雨雪天气。12月为最干燥的月份，月均降雨量仅为{{Convert|61|mm|in|abbr=on}}，月均5.5天为雨雪天气。<ref name=MeteoSchweiz> {{cite web | url =http://www.meteoswiss.admin.ch/web/de/klima/klima_schweiz/tabellen.html | title =Temperature and Precipitation Average Values-Table, 1961-1990 | accessdate =8 May 2009 | 4 = | publisher =Federal Office of Meteorology and Climatology - MeteoSwiss | language=de,fr,it| deadurl =yes | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20090627163841/http://www.meteoswiss.admin.ch/web/de/klima/klima_schweiz/tabellen.html | archivedate =2009年6月27日 }}，气象站海拔366米。</ref>

